Pre-requisites:

1. Get Tuya IPC SDK tarball. You may need to contact Tuya to get the file.
2. Untar Tuya IPC SDK to a directory of your choice.
3. Define a environment variable "TUYA_IPC_SDK_DIR" pointing to the directory containing the SDK.
   During build flow, two directories will be used.
   - $TUYA_IPC_SDK_DIR/include
   - $TUYA_IPC_SDK_DIR/libs

Building the application:

1. Simply type "make clean && make"

